text:
1
Columbia Street, east side, north from Nelson Street. The point of vantage is Dwight Street, which meets Columbia Street at this point. The four-story house is at the S. E. corner of Luqueer Street.

October 21, 1939

P. L. Sperr

2
The east side of Columbia Street, south from Luqueer to Nelson Streets. The four-story house is the same as the one in View 1.

October 21, 1939

P. L. Sperr

View 3: January 10, 1941
